1. **Plan Mode**: reference `docs/vision.md` for alignment, confirm the checkpoint is complete and gather inputs (test names from @Pixel, implementation notes, Connection Guide updates). **Make design decisions based on brand guidelines** - don't ask for approval on UI/UX choices when brand ethos is clear.
